  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Taking On-Rails Shooters Off Rails</h2>Dead Containment is an on-rails shooter inspired by classic arcade light gun games. Players fend off the undead as they race through a city under siege, blasting away the horrors that roam the streets.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/f893b9dd7dd871f3e6bce024c862192e.poster.avif?t=1666480004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/f893b9dd7dd871f3e6bce024c862192e.webm?t=1666480004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/f893b9dd7dd871f3e6bce024c862192e.mp4?t=1666480004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play solo or with a friend over online play, collect hidden pickups to boost your score, rise up the online leaderboards and prove to your friends why you would survive a zombie outbreak.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solo and Online Co-op<br></li><li>Light gun support<br></li><li>Boss fights<br></li><li>Multiple paths - Player chosen and hidden paths<br></li><li>Rankings<br></li><li>Online leaderboards<br></li><li>2 game modes - Arcade and 1 Credit mode<br></li><li>A classic arcade experience</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/202fd1fbc259b2b68d90169b9582385d.poster.avif?t=1666480004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/202fd1fbc259b2b68d90169b9582385d.webm?t=1666480004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302230/extras/202fd1fbc259b2b68d90169b9582385d.mp4?t=1666480004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coming Soon</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More levels<br></li><li>Achievements<br></li><li>Armoury<br></li><li>Full controller support</li></ul>",
